    "description": "<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321580/extras/ee284514ffe993acee071788bb5eef93.webp?t=1725538607\" width=616 height=53 /></span><br><br>在风暴驭使：改变之风中，加入莉莉的行列吧！她是第一位感知到元素风暴来临的法师。掌握威力强大的法术的同时，你还得承担暴露在危险之中的风险。尝试并开发属于你自己的玩法吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挥舞威力强大的魔法与黑暗生物战斗</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321580/extras/2d3f866b181779654c7881d90536008e.poster.avif?t=1725538607\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321580/extras/2d3f866b181779654c7881d90536008e.webm?t=1725538607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321580/extras/2d3f866b181779654c7881d90536008e.mp4?t=1725538607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>准备好与游荡在森林中的的危险怪物对抗。注意了！由于古代魔法的影响，它们变得比以往更强大。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >冒险取胜</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321580/extras/c1b41c7a41aa5a445e3ea7f911ea507c.poster.avif?t=1725538607\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321580/extras/c1b41c7a41aa5a445e3ea7f911ea507c.webm?t=1725538607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321580/extras/c1b41c7a41aa5a445e3ea7f911ea507c.mp4?t=1725538607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>取胜的唯一方法就是勇敢地承担风险。在最后一刻躲避怪物的攻击或是触发森林中的各种陷阱来击败对手。千万当心，一失足成千古恨！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >揭开元素风暴背后的秘密</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321580/extras/1a5e33c6ef40d4be6a413c3f457ba2ca.poster.avif?t=1725538607\" width=616 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321580/extras/1a5e33c6ef40d4be6a413c3f457ba2ca.webm?t=1725538607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321580/extras/1a5e33c6ef40d4be6a413c3f457ba2ca.mp4?t=1725538607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>扮演被誉为当世奇才的女巫莉莉，找出引起元素风暴循环的祸源。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Rogue-lite 核心玩法，搭配高风险操作的技能系统<br></li><li>独特的无冷却时间战斗系统<br></li><li>精美的像素风格和引人入胜的场景设计<br></li><li>支持手柄操作</li></ul>",
